    p(style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 20px;")
        | We’ve sent you a confirmation email. Please check your inbox and click the confirmation link.
    p(style="text-align: center; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 10px;")
        | Didn’t receive the email? Check your spam folder or&nbsp;
        a(href="/users/resend-confirmation" style="color: #3498db; text-decoration: none;") resend the confirmation email.
    div(style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;")
        a(href="/" class="btn btn-secondary" style="padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; background-color: #7f8c8d; color: white;")
